hang of a
Homonym Number:
Word Class: adverb
Sense Number:
Definition:(intensive) as adv. very; also as adj. very great, very fine; = hell/heck of a


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See: also hangashin, heckashin
Pronunciation:
